::KitKat::

She hears the voice and looks around. She heard Phobia, but didn't 
see him.  She shook her head as he said to, but she felt more like 
she was loosing her mind.  She turned and looked at Megatron. She 
walked over and whispered to him. "Don't ask me how, but I got an 
idea.  we might want to go to Phobia's ship."
She felt like an idiot doing this, but her gut feeling told her to go 
through with it.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, cyberwolf4@p... wrote:
> Phobia checks the baby on Kit Kat and hears Megatrons voice.
> "Ah slag this could ruin everything if Kit Kat loses her nerve." He 
> activated his comm on a direct link to his baby.
> 
> His baby crawled up and clamped onto her fur just outside her 
> ear. "Kit Kat this is Phobia, I know you can't respond so listen to 
> me find a way to get yourself and the others to my ship, If you 
want 
> your plan to work you'll have to do exactly as I say. Shake your 
head 
> like you have a bug flying around you if you understand."
